    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Preheat the grill to medium-high</p><p>Drain the <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>drained sweetcorn </strong>to the pan and cook for 2-3 min</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
