    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the tortillas are cooking, chop the<strong> sweet pointed pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper </strong>to the pan with the sweetcorn and cook for 1 min</p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>cannellini beans</strong></p>",
